{"tid":1111544,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"比隻蝻撞車頭","createTime":"2019-04-17T03:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T01:16:15.000Z","uid":94970,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7bb6b0d8d7a757266fc6b5117228acef4a7234","tid":1111544,"uid":94970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"泊完車，諗住坐多陣先走，然後前面黎左架貨van，泊左好耐都未泊得掂，又上壆又唔岩位，最後仲要越褪越後，撞埋落我車頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n落車屌鳩佢，原來係隻蝻黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又唔認錯又唔想賠，最後傾唔掂數報警。而家過左兩星期警察話聯絡唔到佢，叫我帶埋車cam片去錄口供，睇下夠唔夠證據。<br />\n<br />\n其實咁樣落去係咪有排搞？但我有晒車cam，見到佢個蝻樣串柒柒就想搞大佢。"},{"pid":"3d38442bcb8d59b2976069980c8c377c0e03ac09","tid":1111544,"uid":201640,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"隻蝻返鄉下你吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece717bd28a1feef14e29fa169840d2ba628e8eb","tid":1111544,"uid":94970,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"3d38442bcb8d59b2976069980c8c377c0e03ac09","tid":1111544,"uid":201640,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"隻蝻返鄉下你吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:20:22.000Z","msg":"似住香港好耐 識講廣東話<br />\n<br />\n叫佢賠1000都唔肯，而家晒多咁多時間，想claim佢多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fbaf5e21a6038e318a6c07b34518b4770513af","tid":1111544,"uid":195714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ece717bd28a1feef14e29fa169840d2ba628e8eb","tid":1111544,"uid":94970,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"3d38442bcb8d59b2976069980c8c377c0e03ac09","tid":1111544,"uid":201640,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"隻蝻返鄉下你吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:20:22.000Z","msg":"